name: Tic-tac-toe
body:
# Tic Tac Toe - Written using AngularJS

I wrote this application to teach myself [AngularJS](http://angularjs.org/).  The game is very
well-known - at least in Western countries - every schoolchild learns it.  And it's probably
some sort of early developmental milestone to realize that played properly, it is virtually
impossible to lose.  Thus, I think most of us lose interest in it as it's a game notorious
for draws.
